transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on print shop.
This video is regarding e-mail templates and notification enhancements in version 7.3.
Here are all enhancements as e-mail keys and help updated traits.
Manage notification e-mail template structure, e-mail signature and e-mail content update.
Let's see all updates in admin.
Here you can see help is available with each e-mail template.
Along with every e-mail, we have added traits indicating who will receive a copy of the e-mail along with its primary receiver.
Moving ahead, for manage e-mail notification, for the e-mail sent to the customer, we've added a new column under the Set e-mail notification Notify to Customer.
You can enable slash disable the notification for the customer and admin.
Also, for the e-mail templates not sent to customers, this column is kept blank, thus eliminating any room of confusion.
Next is e-mail template structure enhancement.
Previously there were only two things logo and body content.
But now we have given variable for a better UI presentation.
This time we have introduced signature button where one can define signature for customer e-mail, admin e-mail, corporate admin e-mail and corporate customer e-mail.
The last update is that we have updated all e-mail content this time.
If you have any query please contact us at support at onprintshop.
